After a second though, in this case, shouldn't the response include all the entities with an empty `components` property? Assuming that when `strict=false` `components`/optional` don't have a different meaning in practice.

```json
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 0,
  "result": [
    { "components": {}, "entity": 4294967297 },
    ...
    { "components": {}, "entity": 4294967301 }
  ]
}
```
